entries.journal_entry_description: Travel to Talus and find the missing supplies.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Travel to Talus and find the crash site. The crash site waypoint has been placed in your datapad by Kaythree.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Find the 3rd of 5 missing crates around the crash site.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Find the 2nd of 5 missing crates around the crash site.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Find the 1st of 5 missing crates around the crash site.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Find the 5th of 5 missing crates around the crash site.
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Find the 4th of 5 missing crates around the crash site.
entries.task11_journal_entry_title: Find the missing Imperial supply crates at the crash site.
entries.task12_comm_message_text: You have the crates of components and a requistion. If you haven't already, read the requisition and craft the finished product. When done, return everything to the Supply Officer here in Theed.
entries.task12_journal_entry_description: You received a communication from Kaythree as to what to do next.
entries.task13_journal_entry_description: Craft the supplies using the requisition and components found at the crash site.
entries.task14_journal_entry_description: Give the Supply Officer the crate you crafted.
entries.task14_journal_entry_title: Give the Supply Officer the Crate
